Hello Everyone,

Its been a while since I have posted any offers, so I wanted to introduce the new smaller plans that we have been able to now offer at our Canadian Location and also introduce you to some of our offers on yearly plans, with it being January and a great time to buy a VPS for your years projects.

**256MB Plan:**

256MB Ram&lt;br&gt;
50GB Disk Space&lt;br&gt;
